div(class="box col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8 lightbox")
  h1 Start
  h3
    | Create your first Ababool web app!

  div(class="box4")

    h4(class="mt30") Ababool on Git hub
    p
      | You can clone the <a href="https://github.com/CiroArtigot/ababool"
      | target="blank">Ababool Repository on Git Hub</a> or
      | install Ababool with the <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/ababool-generator">npm Ababool App generator</a> (recommended).

    h4(class="mt30") Get Ababool by running...
    pre
      | $ sudo npm install -g ababool-generator
      | $ ababool myapp
      | $ cd myapp
      | $ npm install
      | $ gulp
      | $ npm start

    h4(class="mt30") Prerequisite technologies
    p
      | Ababool is a MEAN Full-Satck solution, do you must install NodeJS and MongoDB before.

    h4(class="mt30") Prerequisite packages
    p
      | Ababool uses Gulp and Bower, so you would need to install both:
    pre
      | $ sudo npm install -g gulp
      | $ sudo npm install -g bower
